text: "Doo Doo Doo Doo Doo (Heartbreaker)" is a 1973 song by English rock band The Rolling Stones and taken from their album Goats Head Soup. It went to number 15 in the United States and number 16 in Sweden. Category:1973 songs Category:The Rolling Stones songs Category:Hard rock songs Category:Funk rock songs
title: Doo Doo Doo Doo Doo (Heartbreaker)
